  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients will have simultaneous Transesophageal Echo (TEE) and Transcranial Doppler (TCD)
      performed and a comparison of timing, sensitivity and intensity of intravenously injected
      bubbles will be determined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
